Eurynomous, 29 Necromancer<br>
Qaedain, 29 magician<br>
<br>
We decided to pet duel because we were bored waiting for giants to spawn in FM. So we had a pet duel to the death, I each gave our pets 2 sword of runes for the procs. I first tried it with an earth pet, seeing as the earth pet had low AGI, he never procced, and died while the necro pet had 90% left. Then I told him that the earth was weak, didn't hit for much, and had really low AGI. So I switched to air...My air pet stunned the bejesus out of Eury's pet, and procced count 'em 6 times during the fight, necro pet procced twice. His pet went down with mine at 45% health.<br>
<br>
Subsequently, he's now level 35, and I'm 33, and I'm going to duel him again with him having the stronger pet.<br>
<br>
